<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{بَلْ تُؤْثِرُونَ الْحَيَاةَ الدُّنْيَا *وَالآخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ وَأَبْقَى}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
